#. module: coal_petroleum
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:coal_petroleum.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<strong><font style=\"color: rgb(255, 156, 0);\">Allowed Quantity</font></strong>: The Allowed quantity is determined through an automated action called \"Allowed Quantity on Transfer.\" This action calculates the quantity by\n"
"               subtracting the tolerance percentage from the demand quantity of the receipt transfer. (Studio)"
msgstr ""
"<strong><font style=\"color: rgb(255, 156, 0);\">ຈຳນວນທີ່ອະນຸຍາດ</font></strong>"
": ຈຳນວນທີ່ອະນຸຍາດແມ່ນຖືກກຳນົດຜ່ານການເຮັດວຽກອັດຕະໂນມັດທີ່ເອີ້ນວ່າ \"Allowed Quantity on "
"Transfer.\" ການເຮັດວຽກນີ້ຈະຄິດໄລ່ຈຳນວນໂດຍການ\n"
"               ລົບເປີເຊັນຄ່າຜິດດ່ຽງອອກຈາກຈຳນວນທີ່ຕ້ອງການໃນການຮັບສິນຄ້າ. (Studio)"

#. module: coal_petroleum
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:coal_petroleum.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<strong><font style=\"color: rgb(255, 156, 0);\">Quality Parameters</font></strong>: The field was created in accordance with the standards and requirements of the coal industry, encompassing a range of tests and\n"
"               parameters. (Studio)"
msgstr ""
"<strong><font style=\"color: rgb(255, 156, 0);\">ພາຣາມິເຕີຄຸນນະພາບ</font></"
"strong>: ຫ້ອງຂໍ້ມູນນີ້ຖືກສ້າງຂຶ້ນຕາມມາດຕະຖານ ແລະ ຂໍ້ກຳນົດຂອງອຸດສາຫະກຳຖ່ານຫີນ, ເຊິ່ງລວມເອົາຊຸດຂອງກ"
"ານທົດສອບ ແລະ\n"
"               ພາຣາມິເຕີຕ່າງໆ. (Studio)"

#. module: coal_petroleum
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:coal_petroleum.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<strong><font style=\"color: rgb(255, 156, 0);\">Tolerance</font></strong>: Tolerance is a field that has been created on the purchase form, allowing us to define a tolerance percentage. refers to minimizing the environmental\n"
"               impact associated with the transportation of coal from mines to end-users. (Studio)"
msgstr ""
"<strong><font style=\"color: rgb(255, 156, 0);\">ຄ່າຜິດດ່ຽງ (Tolerance)</font></"
"strong>: Tolerance ແມ່ນຫ້ອງຂໍ້ມູນທີ່ຖືກສ້າງຂຶ້ນໃນແບບຟອມການຊື້, ເພື່ອໃຫ້ພວກເຮົາກຳນົດເປີເຊັນຄ່າຜິດດ່ຽງ"
"ໄດ້. ເຊິ່ງກ່ຽວຂ້ອງກັບການຫຼຸດຜ່ອນຜົນກະທົບຕໍ່ສິ່ງແວດລ້ອມ\n"
"               ທີ່ເກີດຈາກການຂົນສົ່ງຖ່ານຫີນຈາກບໍ່ແຮ່ໄປຫາຜູ້ໃຊ້ສຸດທ້າຍ. (Studio)"

#. module: coal_petroleum
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:coal_petroleum.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<strong><font style=\"color: rgb(255, 156, 0);\">Vehicle Number</font>: </strong>It is required to provide the vehicle number for the purpose of formal documentation. Please ensure that the vehicle number associated with the\n"
"               selected transportation mode, whether it is a Truck, Ship, or Train, is accurately provided. (Studio)"
msgstr ""
"<strong><font style=\"color: rgb(255, 156, 0);\">ເລກທະບຽນລົດ</font>: </strong>"
"ຈຳເປັນຕ້ອງລະບຸເລກທະບຽນລົດເພື່ອຈຸດປະສົງໃນການເຮັດເອກະສານທາງການ. ກະລຸນາຮັບປະກັນວ່າ ເລກທະບຽນລົດ"
"ທີ່ກ່ຽວຂ້ອງກັບ\n"
"               ຮູບແບບການຂົນສົ່ງທີ່ເລືອກ, ບໍ່ວ່າຈະເປັນ ລົດບັນທຸກ, ເຮືອ, ຫຼື ລົດໄຟ, ແມ່ນໄດ້ຖືກລະບຸຢ່າງ"
"ຖືກຕ້ອງ. (Studio)"

